---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const curriculumUrl = "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VBkWbmi9Pjx7BVrrSfI872oBf-D52YQD/view";
---

<Layout
  title="Sobre Mí | Jasmany Franco"
  description="Conoce más sobre Jasmany Franco, Ingeniero en Sistemas y Full Stack Developer."
>
  <section class="w-full pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- ─── BIO ─── -->
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mb-4">
        Sobre <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">Mí</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full mb-8"></div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--hero-desc)] mb-4">
        Ingeniero en Sistemas con trayectoria consolidada en la administración y optimización de
        infraestructura tecnológica en el sector público. Mi enfoque actual es el desarrollo de
        software moderno con el stack
        <strong class="text-[var(--hero-text)]"> Node.js y React</strong>, transformando
        procesos manuales en soluciones digitales eficientes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--hero-desc)] mb-16">
        Profesional orientado a la resolución de problemas técnicos bajo presión, con capacidad de
        liderazgo probada y un compromiso constante con el aprendizaje autodidacta.
      </p>

      <!-- ─── EXPERIENCIA ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mb-4">
        Experiencia <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">Laboral</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full mb-8"></div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)] mb-20">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-3">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">
              GAD Municipal del cantón Naranjal
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[var(--accent)]">
              Analista de Sistemas / Full Stack Developer
            </p>
          </div>
          <span
            class="text-xs font-semibold text-[var(--muted)] px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Abril 2014 - Actualidad
          </span>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--hero-desc)]">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shrink-0"></span>
            Liderazgo técnico del departamento en múltiples periodos, coordinando equipos y
            asesorando en la toma de decisiones tecnológicas.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--hero-desc)]">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shrink-0"></span>
            Desarrollo de sistemas full-stack en producción: Gestión Documental (DMS), Cash
            Management y Futbol System.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--hero-desc)]">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shrink-0"></span>
            Implementación de infraestructura tecnológica: VPNs, virtualización con Proxmox,
            certificados SSL y control de asistencia.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--hero-desc)]">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shrink-0"></span>
            Integración de pagos con el Banco Central del Ecuador y soporte remoto a los GAD
            de Limón Indanza y Balao.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]"
            >React</span
          >
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]"
            >Node.js</span
          >
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]"
            >PostgreSQL</span
          >
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]"
            >TypeScript</span
          >
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]"
            >Docker</span
          >
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]"
            >Proxmox</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ─── HABILIDADES TÉCNICAS ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mb-4">
        Habilidades <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">Técnicas</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full mb-8"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--accent)] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">
            Frontend
          </h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">React</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">TailwindCSS</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Astro</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">HTML5/CSS3</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--accent)] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">
            Backend
          </h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Node.js</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Express</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Sequelize</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Prisma</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">API REST</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--accent)] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">
            Bases de Datos
          </h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">MySQL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--accent)] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">
            DevOps & Herramientas
          </h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Docker</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Git</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Linux</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-[var(--tag)] text-[var(--tag-text)]">Proxmox</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ─── HABILIDADES BLANDAS ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mb-4">
        Habilidades <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">Blandas</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full mb-8"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-20">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-light)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--accent)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 0 0-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 0 1 5.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 0 1 9.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">Liderazgo</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--hero-desc)] mt-0.5">Coordinación de equipos técnicos y dirección de departamento.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-light)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--accent)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 0 0-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 0 0 8.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128m0 0a15.998 15.998 0 0 0 3.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 0 1 1.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 0 0 4.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 0 0-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 0 0-4.649 4.763m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 0 0-3.42-3.42" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">Resolución de Problemas</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--hero-desc)] mt-0.5">Capacidad analítica para diagnosticar y resolver bajo presión.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-light)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--accent)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 0 0 1.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 0 1-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 0 1-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 0 1-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.823 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 1 0-7.517 0c.85.493 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">Aprendizaje Autodidacta</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--hero-desc)] mt-0.5">Actualización constante en nuevas tecnologías y tendencias.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-light)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--accent)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">Trabajo en Equipo</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--hero-desc)] mt-0.5">Colaboración interdisciplinaria y soporte a otros GADs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-light)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--accent)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6Zm0 9.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.75 18v-2.25ZM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 20.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6Zm0 9.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 20.25h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 13.5 18v-2.25Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">Adaptabilidad</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--hero-desc)] mt-0.5">Experiencia multisectorial: desarrollo, infraestructura, soporte.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-light)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--accent)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)]">Comunicación Efectiva</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--hero-desc)] mt-0.5">Redacción técnica clara y comunicación con equipos multidisciplinarios.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ─── FORMACIÓN ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mb-4">
        Formación
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full mb-8"></div>

      <!-- timeline -->
      <div class="relative mb-20">
        <div class="absolute left-[7px] top-2 bottom-2 w-0.5 bg-[var(--accent)]/30"></div>

        <div class="relative pl-10 pb-10">
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-1.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] ring-4 ring-[var(--bg)]"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[var(--accent)] tracking-wider uppercase">2013 — 2017</span>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mt-1">Universidad de Guayaquil</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--hero-desc)]">Ingeniero en Sistemas Computacionales</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted)] mt-1">Reg. SENESCYT: 1006-2017-1872471</p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-10">
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-1.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] ring-4 ring-[var(--bg)]"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[var(--accent)] tracking-wider uppercase">2022 — 2024</span>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-[var(--hero-text)] mt-1">Formación Continua</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--hero-desc)]">Docker, React + TypeScript, JavaScript Moderno, Git + GitHub, CSS Grid + Flexbox, Bootstrap 5, Desarrollo Web Completo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ─── CTA ─── -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href={curriculumUrl}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold
            bg-[var(--accent)] text-white
            hover:brightness-110 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[var(--accent)]/25
            active:scale-95 transition-all"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
            <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline>
            <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
          </svg>
          Descargar CV
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/Darkjasmany"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-semibold
            border border-[var(--border)] text-[var(--hero-text)]
            hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)]
            active:scale-95 transition-all"
        >
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path
              d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Ver GitHub
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
